headline: Kohl's (KSS) Beats Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Kohl's (KSS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 31.94% and 0.94%, respectively, for the quarter ended January 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
